needed pythonmodules:
 * twisted
 * python-twisted-words
 * python-twisted-conch
 * python-twisted-web
 * python-yaml
 * python-pyopenssl
 * python-crypto

optional:
 * python-feedparser
 * python-svn
 * pyxmltv
 * pywapi (http://code.google.com/p/python-weather-api/)
Gentoo:
emerge twisted-words pyyaml
for remoteCliServer:
emerge twisted-conch

The bot is started with
> twistd otfbot -c otfbot.yaml
from the root-dir of the project